@startuml login_user_sd
title UC 2.1.2 - Prijava korisnika (Glavni tok)

actor "Registrovani korisnik" as U
participant "Frontend (React)" as FE
participant "Backend API (Express)" as BE
database "MySQL" as DB

U -> FE: Otvara stranicu za prijavu
FE -> U: Prikazuje formu za unos emaila i lozinke

U -> FE: Unosi email i lozinku
U -> FE: Klik na "Prijavi se"
FE -> BE: POST /auth/login (email, lozinka)
BE -> DB: Dohvata korisnika po emailu
DB --> BE: Podaci o korisniku
BE -> BE: Provera lozinke
BE --> FE: 200 OK + JWT cookie/token
FE -> U: Prikaz poÄetne stranice
@enduml
